<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>بَابُ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>المَفْعُولِ مِنْ أَجْلِهِ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span style="color:#006d98">وَهُوَ:</span> الِاسْمُ المَنْصُوبُ الَّذِي يُذْكَرُ بَيَاناً لِسَبَبِ وُقُوعِ الفِعْلِ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span style="color:#006d98">نَحْوُ قَوْلِكَ:</span> قَامَ زَيْدٌ إِجْلَالاً لِعَمْرٍو، وَقَصَدْتُكَ ابْتِغَاءَ مَعْرُوفِكَ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
